title: Let's Watch TV: Wedding Coach
description:
This week Joe and Fran watch the Netflix reality show The Wedding Coach. Joe and Fran share real life wedding travesties from the annals of the Dombrowski family history books and digest this interesting show about wedding train wrecks.
